snippet.title: Trance of OMI - #TheyCallHimOG | Pawan Kalyan | Emraan Hashmi | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Danayya
snippet.description:
A sound that SPELLS FEAR 🧿

OMI arrives with his trance… 🔥
#TranceOfOMI

#OG #TheyCallHimOG #OGonSept25

Music : Thaman S
Programmed & Arranged by - Thaman S
Beat & EDM works - Beyond Sound (T) 
Electric Guitars - Subhashree 
Additional Programming - Shashank Alamuru, Osho V & Hari S R

Lyrics : Adviteeya Vojjala

Chorus: Sruthi Ranjani, Adviteeya, Pranati, Sruthika, Pratyusha, Girija & Soujanya

snippet.title: CYCLE WALI DIDI I साईकिल वाली दीदी I AAMRAPALI DUBEY I OFFICIAL TRAILER I BHOJPURI MOVIE 2025
snippet.description:
#aamrapalidubey #shivamtiwari #bhupendrasingh #pushpendrasingh #anuojha #sweetysingh #satyendrasingh #omjha #swastika #dholu #cyclewalididi #aamrapalifanpage #trailer #trending 

IVY ENTERTAINMENT PRESENTS IN ASSOCIATION WITH NEELABH TIWARI FILMS (OPC) Pvt Ltd. 
फ़िल्म - साईकिल वाली दीदी 
आम्रपली  दुबे , शिवम्  तिवारी , भूपेंद्र  सिंह ,  संतोष  श्रीवास्त्व , अनु  ओझा , स्वीटी सिंह , पुष्पेंद्र  सिंह , पल्लवी  कोहली
बाल कलाकार - स्वस्तिका, ढोलू
कांसेप्ट - संदीप सिंह
निर्देशक – इश्तियाक शैख़ बंटी
लेखक – सत्येंद्र सिंह
 संगीतकार- ओम झा 
गीतकार – प्यारे लाल यादव
 संकलन - प्रीतम नायक
 छायांकन- दिलीप कुमार शर्मा 
कोरियोग्राफर - कानू मुख़र्जी , सोनू प्रीतम
 पोस्ट प्रोडक्शन -  3 स्टूडियो
पार्शव संगीत वो मिक्सिंग – राजेश प्रसाद
ट्रेलर -विकास पवार
आर्ट डायरेक्टर - अंजनी तिवारी 
निर्माता - संदीप सिंह, नीलाभ तिवारी 
,सॅटॅलाइट और डिजिटल पार्टनर - B4U भोजपुरी 
म्यूजिक – IVY म्यूजिक
B4U क्रिएटिव टीम – मारुद शर्मा, नेहा उपाध्याय , विशाल यादव
 B4U लीगल - संदीप राणा , तृष्णा पटेल , पूनम शिंदे , आकांक्षा वाकोडे – मोरे
 ऑफिस बॉय - कन्हैया झा
 IVY – एंटरटेनमेंट – फाइनेंस -  प्रदीप के दागा , जिनेले मैस्करेन्हास , विपुल जैन , निवृत्ति पाटिल , गणेश महादेव टापरे, हिमांशु चौधरी , राहुल सिरोया
B4U – फाइनेंस  -  संतोष गर्ग , रविंदर साल्वी , साक्षी शैलार 


Film – CYCLE WALI DIDI 
Cast: AAMRAPLI DUBEY, SHIVAM TIWARI, BHUPENDRA SINGH,  SANTOSH SRIVASATVA, ANU OJHA, SWEETYSINGH, PUSHPENDRA SINGH, PALLAVI KOHLI 
Child artist – Swastika , Dholu 
 Concept: Sandeep Singh
 Director: Ishtiyaque Shaikh Bunty
 Writer : SATYENDRA SINGH
 Music Director: Om Jha 
Lyrics: Pyare Lal Yadav
 Editor: PREETAM NAYAK 
Cinematographer: Dilip Kumar Sharma 
Choreographer: Kanu Mukherjee & Sonu Pritam 
Postproduction: 3 Studio
Background & Mixing: Rajesh prasad 
Art Director: Anjani Tiwari 
Producers: Sandeep Singh, Neelabh Tiwari 
Satellite, and Digital Partner: B4U Bhojpuri
Music- IVY Music 
 B4U Creative Team: Marud Sharma, Neha Upadhyay, Vishal Yadav, Nishi rai
 B4U Legal Team: Sandeep Rana, Trishna Patel, Poonam Shinde, Akanksha Wakode-More 
Office Boy: Kanhaiya Jha

🎬 Movie Credits:
Movie: Saiyaara
Starring: Ahaan Panday, Aneet Padda
Director: Mohit Suri
Producer: Akshaye Widhani
Director of Photography: Vikas Sivaraman
Story And Screenplay: Sankalp Sadanah
Dialogues: Rohan Shankar
Associate Producer: Rishabh Chopra
Creative Executive Producer: Sumana Ghosh
Music: Mithoon, Sachet-Parampara, Rishabh Kant, Vishal Mishra, Tanishk Bagchi, Faheem Abdullah, Arslan Nizami
Lyrics: Irshad Kamil, Mithoon, Rishabh Kant, Raj Shekhar
Editors: Devendra Murdeshwar, Rohit Makwana
Production Designers: Laxmi Keluskar, Rajat Poddar
Director of Choreography: Vijay A Ganguly
Costume Designer: Sheetal Sharma
Supervising Producer: Gurpreet Singh
Sound: Manas Choudhury, Ganesh Gangadharan
Background Music: John Stewart Eduri
Action Director: Aejaz Gulab
Casting Director: Shanoo Sharma
Visual Effects Studio: yFX
Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney
Release Date: 18 July 2025

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.description:
पनवाड़ी… ke peechhe wali patli gali,
Mein hai tumhare sajan ki कोठरी!

Get ready to turn up the देसी flavor with ‘Panwadi’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’! 🍃 Featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf and Sanya Malhotra in the music video, the song is sung by Khesari Lal Yadav, Masoom Sharma, Dev Negi, Pritam, Nikhita Gandhi and AKASA. Written by Jairaj and composed by A.P.S., this earworm will turn up the heat at any party! 🔥🎧

snippet.title: Marvel Animation's Marvel Zombies - Official Trailer #2 (2025) Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd
snippet.description:
Check out the Trailer #2 for Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies, an animated horror installment to the Marvel Cinematic Universe distributed by Marvel Studios. This series re-contextualizes the Marvel Universe as Earth's mightiest heroes go head-to-head against a zombie outbreak, turning even the strongest of them into undead nightmares. Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

After the Avengers are overtaken by a zombie plague, a desperate group of survivors discover the key to bringing an end to the super-powered undead, racing across a dystopian landscape and risking life and limb to save their world. 
 
Marvel Zombies stars Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd, Florence Pugh, David Harbour, Tessa Thompson, Simu Liu, Awkwafina, Hailee Steinfeld, Wyatt Russell, Randall Park, Iman Vellani, Dominique Thorne, and more. The series is executive produced by Kevin Feige, Louis D’Esposito, Brad Winderbaum, Dana Vasquez-Eberhardt, Bryan Andrews, and Zeb Wells, and is produced by Danielle Costa, Carrie Wassenaar. 

Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

#MarvelZombies #Marvel #IGN

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Video Song | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the video song of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

snippet.title: 🇮🇳 Gukesh D vs Divya Deshmukh 🇮🇳 | FIDE Grand Swiss 2025 | Round 8 | Board 57
snippet.description:
🤩 The FIDE Grand Swiss and FIDE Women’s Grand Swiss 2025 are underway in 🇺🇿 Samarkand, Uzbekistan! From September 4 to 15, the historic city on the Silk Road has become the center of the chess world.

The stakes are sky-high: the top two finishers in the Grand Swiss will qualify for the 2026 Candidates Tournament, while the Women’s Grand Swiss will determine two spots for the 2026 Women’s Candidates.

Eleven rounds of uncompromising battles are being played under the Swiss System, with 172 participants from all continents — 116 in the Grand Swiss and 56 in the Women’s Grand Swiss.

The total prize fund is $855,000, with $625,000 for the Grand Swiss and $230,000 for the Women’s Grand Swiss.

🔗 Pairings: https://grandswiss2025.fide.com/open/

snippet.title: Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song | Rakshakudu | Nagarjuna, Sushmita Sen | A.R. Rahman |Udit Narayan
snippet.description:
Listen & Enjoy the Melodious Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song from Rakshakudu Movie. Featuring Nagarjuna & Sushmita Sen, with Music by A.R. Rahman. Sung by Udit Narayan, P. Unnikrishnan & Harini, Lyrics by Bhuvanachandra, and Directed by Praveen Gandhi.

Song Details:
Song Name: Soniya Soniya
Singers: P. Unnikrishnan, Udit Narayan, Harini
Lyrics: Bhuvanachandra
Music Director: A.R. Rahman

Movie Details:
Movie Name: Rakshakudu
Banner: J.R.S. Combines
Producer: J. Rama Chandra Rao
Director: Praveen Gandhi
Audio On: Aditya Music.

Soniya Soniya Song Telugu Lyrics:

సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా ఆఆ
సోనియా సోనియా స్వీటు స్వీటు సోనియా రేగుతోంది లేత వయసు జోరు  
ఘాటు లవ్వు  రెండు టైపు నీటుదొకటి  నాటుదొకటి
రెండిట్లో ఏది నీకు ప్యారు
Sometimes  నీటే స్వీటు… Sometimes నాటే రైటు…
పిల్ల కళ్ళని చూసీ చేసేయ్ గురువా ఫైటు   || సోనియా|| 2
పువ్వుల్ని తడిమే చిరుగాలి మల్లె చెక్కిళ్ళు తడితే అది నీటు
కొమ్మల్ని విరిచే సుడిగాలి మల్లె ఒడి చేర్చుకుంటే అది నాటు
పచ్చిక మీద పడే చినుకుల మల్లె చిరు ముద్దులు పెట్టి శృతి చేయడమే నీటు
కసిగా మీద పడే ఉప్పన్నమల్లే చెలి పైటని పట్టి చిత్తు చేయడమే నాటు
నీ కురుల మీద పువ్వుని నేనై మురిపించే ఆట ఆడించనా
మృదువైన ముద్దుల్లో సొగసే ఉందే మంచంలో మాటలకి చోటేముందే
మత్తెక్కి కౌగిట్లో ముంచేస్తా అమ్మడు || సోనియా||
 
ఊరించే ఒడిలో  ఉపొంగే తడిలో బుగల్ని ఎంచక్కా పిండేస్తుంటే
పరువాల పిలుపే కళ్ళలో మెరుపై గుండెల్లో సెగలే రగిలిస్తుంటే
కౌగిలి క్రికెట్కి సిస్టమ్ లేదే అంపైరు లేడే మగతనముంటే చాలే
పట్టి పడతోస్తే వేగేదెట్టా బరువాపేదెట్టా ఎద మల్లెలపూవానోయ్
నలిపైకపోతే అందం లేదే కసి లేని మొహం మొహం కాదే
కోమలితో వాదిస్తే అర్ధం ఉందా కవ్వించి కాటేస్తే న్యాయం ఉందా
ప్రేయసిని గెలిచేది నా చూపుతానమేగా 
||సోనియా||

As the sequel to the gripping Bengali thriller Raktabeej, this track sets the tone for what’s to come in the film’s storyline — filled with mystery, emotion, and cinematic brilliance. Don't miss the chance to witness the magic of Chokher Neele — a musical masterpiece that blends heart-touching lyrics with mesmerizing visuals.

Goddess Mahalakshmi, the deity of wealth and divine grace, is especially worshipped on Fridays (Shukravaram). Listening to her devotional songs on this sacred day is believed to attract prosperity, peace, and happiness into your life.

This video features the soulful bhakti song "Raavamma Mahalakshmi" along with other Friday-special devotional songs in Telugu, perfect for your daily or weekly pooja.

🌸 Why Listen on Fridays?

Invokes Mahalakshmi’s blessings for financial growth

Helps bring peace and harmony to the home

Removes negativity and spiritual obstacles

Ideal for Friday poojas, Lakshmi vratam, and daily bhakti

🎧 Use this during morning or evening prayers, especially on Fridays and auspicious days.

Goddess Lakshmi, the symbol of wealth, prosperity, and divine grace, is especially worshipped on Fridays. Listening to devotional songs on this day is believed to attract peace, abundance, and positive energy into your home.

In this video, enjoy the beautiful Telugu bhakti song "Sowbhagya Lakshmi Raavamma", specially sung to please Goddess Lakshmi and invite her blessings.

🌺 Why listen on Friday (Shukravaram)?

Brings financial stability and prosperity

Invites divine feminine energy into your life

Enhances mental peace and household harmony

Ideal for Friday Lakshmi puja or daily spiritual practice

🎧 Use this song during morning or evening prayer to elevate your devotion and connect with the divine energy of Sri Mahalakshmi.

👉 Subscribe for more Telugu bhakti songs and spiritual content every week!

snippet.title: ಶುಕ್ರವಾರದ ವಿಶೇಷ ಭಕ್ತಿಗೀತೆಗಳು🙏 | ಭಾಗ್ಯದ ಲಕ್ಷ್ಮಿ ಬಾರಮ್ಮ | Friday Laxmi Devi Kannada Bhakti Songs
snippet.description:
🙏 ಶುಕ್ರವಾರದ ವಿಶೇಷ ಭಕ್ತಿಗೀತೆಗಳು | ಭಾಗ್ಯದ ಲಕ್ಷ್ಮಿ ಬಾರಮ್ಮ | Friday Laxmi Devi Kannada Bhakti Songs – A divine collection of Sri Mahalakshmi Devi Kannada devotional songs. Fridays are very auspicious for worshipping Goddess Lakshmi, the giver of wealth and fortune. Listening to these bhakti geethegalu removes financial troubles, brings peace, and fills life with prosperity and happiness.

✨ Benefits of Listening / ಫಲಗಳು:
🔸 Clears financial struggles (ಹಣದ ಸಮಸ್ಯೆ ನಿವಾರಣೆ)
🔸 Attracts prosperity, wealth, and good fortune (ಭಾಗ್ಯ, ಐಶ್ವರ್ಯ)
🔸 Brings harmony and peace at home
🔸 Removes obstacles and hardships
🔸 Invokes blessings of Sri Mahalakshmi Devi

🕉️ Listen to these Lakshmi Devi Kannada Bhakti Songs every Friday with devotion and receive the divine grace of Sri Mahalakshmi.

📌 Don’t forget to Subscribe, Like, and Share for more Kannada devotional songs, stotras, and mantras.

snippet.title: Akshay Kumar, Nupur Sanon - Filhall (8K Lyric Video) |  BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Ammy Virk
snippet.description:
#jaani  #filhall #akshaykumar #bpraak  
Have you ever selflessly loved someone so much that just their smile can brighten up your day? 

FILHALL, a feel good song about love and it’s beauty of never giving up. 

From the makers of iconic songs like Qismat , Maan Bhariya , Pachtaoge  and Coka , one of bollywood most celebrated Artist Akshay Kumar  Featuring Nupur sanon , bring to you, their first ever debut Music video , in the voice of Bpraak . The video , shot is done by the concept king Arvindr Khaira  and penned down by one and only lyrical machine JAANI . Filhaal, a song that depicts the story of that true love which is pious, selfless yet incomplete. 

Desi Melodies proudly presents FILHALL  In association with cape of Good films & Azeem Dayani

snippet.title: VALORANT Champions Paris — Group Stage — Day 1
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group.
